<HL>
   Eastern Indicted
   Over Failures
   In Maintenance
   ----
   By Amy Dockser Marcus and Bridget O'Brian
   Staff Reporters of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
07/26/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE A4
</SO>
